{"tid":930213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】全球最老YouTuber　107歲印度婆婆逝世　「西瓜咖哩雞」最馳名","createTime":"2018-12-06T06:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T09:27:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3404c6371d489f040e5eab011c2de667a015b4f7","tid":930213,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20181206/s00005/1544064792528/【短片】全球最老youtuber-107歲印度婆婆逝世-「西瓜咖哩雞」最馳名\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20181206%2Fs00005%2F1544064792528%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%80%E8%80%81youtuber-107%E6%AD%B2%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%A9%86%E5%A9%86%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E3%80%8C%E8%A5%BF%E7%93%9C%E5%92%96%E5%93%A9%E9%9B%9E%E3%80%8D%E6%9C%80%E9%A6%B3%E5%90%8D&d=OnQhE1jfOhsITLw1mWoZi54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a264fb73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20181206%2Fs00005%2F1544064792528%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%80%E8%80%81youtuber-107%E6%AD%B2%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%A9%86%E5%A9%86%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E3%80%8C%E8%A5%BF%E7%93%9C%E5%92%96%E5%93%A9%E9%9B%9E%E3%80%8D%E6%9C%80%E9%A6%B3%E5%90%8D&h=c662f7d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20181206/s00005/1544064792528/【短片】全球最老youtuber-107歲印度婆婆逝世-「西瓜咖哩雞」最馳名</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181206/s00005/0e38861ebadb7914cef22526c764466f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181206%2Fs00005%2F0e38861ebadb7914cef22526c764466f.jpg&h=8c437c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 印度的馬斯坦娜瑪近日逝世。(影片截圖/明報製圖)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n全球最老的知名YouTuber馬斯坦娜瑪逝世，享年107歲。<br />\n印度的馬斯坦娜瑪（Mastanamma）以烹調傳統美食在YouTube名聲大噪，擁有超過120萬訂閱者，影片觀看次數逾2億，近日其YouTube頻道上載影片，宣布她與世長辭。<br />\n馬斯坦娜瑪和她四代的家人住在安德拉邦古迪瓦達鎮一個偏遠村莊，她的孫子拉克斯曼（Karre Laxman）和其朋友雷迪（Srinath Reddy）是YouTube的網絡名人。拉克斯曼和雷迪在2016年開始為馬斯坦娜瑪拍攝烹飪影片，並在YouTube創立「鄉村美食」（Country Foods）頻道。<br />\n馬斯坦娜瑪的影片大多在露天的農地上拍攝，且用很基本的廚具烹煮印度傳統美食，而最馳名的菜色是「西瓜咖哩雞」。她的影片在YouTube大受歡迎，創立頻道後的幾個月內已有數千名訂閱者，而至今就有超過120萬訂閱者，影片觀看次數逾2億。<br />\n「鄉村美食」頻道周一（3日）上載一條「馬斯坦娜瑪最後的旅程」影片，直播她的送葬儀式，又在周二（4日）發表「願您安息，馬斯坦娜瑪」的下葬影片，正式宣布她與世長辭。頻道在馬斯坦娜瑪去世前6個月停止發布其烹飪影片，可能她當時的健康狀況已經開始不佳。"},{"pid":"74cd47dbca9d579ae9819f90037c8a2562c93721","tid":930213,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a59618a5ddbfd9ee6b43400653ef51e34fbd12","tid":930213,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:10:49.000Z","msg":"107<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667e294c51f40f5398acd885fafb19d95b6c6261","tid":930213,"uid":91736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8d7c0459819c352390ab10ab465c4f7e4703d9","tid":930213,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ce330823b14344d064b4e61d5236c9774a271a","tid":930213,"uid":153497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"西瓜咖哩雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幽默大師原來師承佢"},{"pid":"ebed03b432c49bda47fcadc504014344c9f05b61","tid":930213,"uid":10503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7ce330823b14344d064b4e61d5236c9774a271a","tid":930213,"uid"